Food Fighters US - Season 1, Episode 5




Cortney Anderson-Sanford

Home cook Cortney Anderson-Sanford from Seattle, Washington has brought her best recipes to compete against five professional chefs. A wife and mother of two, Cortney feels confident in the kitchen. Her eldest son has high functioning Autism and she is determined to win enough money to bring him and the rest of their family to Maui.




Original Air Date: 19-Aug-2014
